- Easy-to-use interface

Supermax can reduce the size of video files by up to 90% without affecting their quality. This means you can store more videos on your hard drive or upload them to the cloud without worrying about running out of space.

### How to Use Supermax

Using Supermax is easy. Here are the steps to compress your videos:

1. Download and install Supermax on your computer.
2. Open Supermax and click on the "Add Files" button.
3. Select the video files you want to compress.
4. Choose a compression preset or customize your compression settings.
5. Click the "Compress" button.

Supermax will start compressing your videos. The process may take some time, depending on the size of your video files.
